---
title: Chipotle Black Bean Burrito Bowl with avocado and pico de gallo
description: The burrito is a staple of Tex-Mex cuisine that originates from Ciudad Juárez in Mexico. These plant-based burrito bowls are filled with zesty lime rice, gorgeous green avocado, chipotle black beans, and another Mexican staple—pico de gallo.
